{"about_the_game":"\u00abWhere to, army man? Want to visit Kuznetsk? Yes, I can drive you till the road to it, but I cannot go there. The visits are forbidden. It is a weird place. There was an accident there few years ago, so they control anyone who vants to visit the town. I bring the goods to local market weekly, using special pass from government. But, you know, I have a weird feeling about that place \u2013 it seems like it stuck in the past, like a fly in amber. Also, that creepy lake near town \u2013 they call it Darkness or something. No one swims in there, even in the hottest summer \u2013 locals think it is cursed. \u00bb<br><br><i>This game is a Visual Novel in detective genre, with an original plot, and anime-style graphics. The story goes about a group of teens living in 1997 year, who are encountering a few mysteries about rural Russian town Kuznetsk.<br><br>Full voiceover made by star Russian voice actors.<br><br>This game contains Mature Content: domestic and psychological violence, suicide, blood and light gore.<br><br>This is a work of fiction. Names, characters, places and incidents either are products of the author\u2019s imagination or are used fictitiously. Any resemblance to actual events or locales or persons, living or dead, is entirely coincidental.</i>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Wolf and eggs","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2013120/f0fa17ed8c500391b8389ac47a0901aa5efac0a0.jpg"},{"name":"The Pit","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2013120/c88b247c6dfbe2b3fb31fe2637354edd3eb2c71b.jpg"},{"name":"The Dream","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2013120/6d0a19ba0038865bf47c4cf11626be9514579633.jpg"},{"name":"The Slug","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/2013120/cca8ace0abab35a848fd656c627d63d4a7c785f2.jpg"},{"name":"The Circle","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic